"47:10:11" : {s: 47, a: 10, w: 11, r: "قبل", t: "قَبْلِهِمْ", l: "قَبْل", lc: 242, tl: "qablihim", lb: "পূর্বে",e: "before them", b: "তাদের পূর্ববর্তীদের (মত)", i: "sebelum mereka", f: 29, rm: "to accept/admit/receive/agree, meet anyone, to face/encounter someone/something, advance/approach, correspond, counteract/compare/requite/compensate, the front part (12:26), accept with approval, show favour."},
"47:10:12" : {s: 47, a: 10, w: 12, r: "دمر", t: "دَمَّرَ", l: "دَمَّرَ", lc: 8, tl: "dammara", lb: "ধ্বংস করা",e: "Allah destroyed", b: "ধ্বংস করে দিয়েছেন", i: "membinasakan", f: 1, rm: "To perish utterly, be annihilated, to destroy."},
